Cell["\<\
Provisional 2 - sig (E4) = (12, 18, 16+4m) --> iso=2 --> \
\[LineSeparator]Provisional 2 - sig (E4) = (8, 12, 4+4m) --> iso=2 --> \
\[LineSeparator]Provisional 2 - sig (E4) = (4, 6, 4m-8) 
